Subject: Re: [VB] curtains and curtain rods ?

Got any late-model westies in the local junkyard?  Ifso, you can
pull the curtain rods out of it, and modify them to fit your 
windows - the profile of the extrusion is identical.  Here's what the
early (59->67) westy curtain rod profile looks like:

http://www.calweb.com/~thom/cgi-bin/gallery-search.cgi?string=westy+curtain+rod

